"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?9/5/9299?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Diarrhea in adults (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?34/51/35634?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: High-fiber diet (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?5/55/6006?source=see_link\">",
